lastWompContents: Drop by and see some Brazilian Art! In 4h and a half from now!
So cool! Check Wacko's truck! You can take your car inside! <3
And dont forget to check out our vehicles, at The Philosopher Motors. The best Brazilian wearable designers: Manute, Ghini, Rafaela!
And Enjoy some music at our Optic Store, at Vibes by the Sea!
And, as a final tour, check out our largest Brazilian exhibition of Metaverse. More than 100 Brazilian artists!!
